17) List of Magic Constants (Most Important)
Magic constants are predefined PHP constants commonly used for debugging, logging, and file path management in MVC applications.

Magic Constant	Meaning
__LINE__	Current line number
__FILE__	Full file path
__DIR__	        Directory of the file
__FUNCTION__	Function name
__CLASS__	Class name
__METHOD__	Class method name
__NAMESPACE__	Current namespace

âš¡ Most Asked in Interviews

